data.description:
Welcome to your dream home nestled within the serene Creekwood Estates. This enchanting 3-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom home boasts comfort and luxury. With over 1,900 sqft of living space, this residence offers a blend of elegance and rustic charm. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the warmth of the fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance that invites you to unwind after a long day. The well-appointed kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight. Step outside and be greeted by the allure of your private paradise - an in-ground swimming pool beckons for refreshing dips on sunny days, while two expansive decks offer the perfect spots for entertaining guests or savoring your morning coffee. Situated on 2.6 acres of lush, verdant land, this home provides the ultimate sense of privacy and space. Creekwood Estates offers the best of both worlds - the tranquility of country living coupled with the convenience of being just minutes from the city. Here, you can relish the peaceful seclusion of your own retreat while having easy access to urban amenities, ensuring that you have the ideal lifestyle balance.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours!
